      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have had an initial 10 min, remove the tray from the oven and crush the<strong> potatoes</strong> slightly with a potato masher</p><p>Add the <strong>marinated chicken thighs </strong>to the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a final 22-25 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the potatoes are crispy – these are your <strong>smoky chicken thighs</strong>, <strong>roasted tomato</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>crispy roasties</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-3-1654602030359-x200.jpg",
