    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and chop the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, then cut in half widthways</p><p>Top, tail and chop the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, wash thoroughly, then cut in half widthways</p><p>Thread the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>courgette </strong>and<strong> leek</strong> widthways onto the <strong>soaked</strong> <strong>skewers</strong>, alternating as you go – these are your<strong> veg skewers</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
