    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>veg skewers</strong> to the pan (flat-side down) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until charred</p><p>Once charred, add a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> to the pan, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 7-8 min or until the veg is tender – these are your <strong>charred veg skewers</strong></p>",
